blog.title: Why hello there...
blog.description: Masterlist Welcome to shenanigans of me! Here you will find anime and KPop as they fleet across my thoughts and feed. I write as well so enjoy!

body:
Upcoming Concerts

So the beginning of May is going to be a very busy time for me. From May 2nd to May 9th, my friend and I are road tripping to California for, not one but two, concerts! We are going to be vlogging it because why not!

We are seeing VAV in San Francisco on May 3rd. These tickets include a fan sign which they’ll be giving us a copy of the new Thrilla Killa mini album for, a group photo, and a hi touch. My friend in top of it bought us snapshot pick a pose pictures with each of the members as well as lightsticks.

Then on May 4th, we’re driving down to Los Angeles to our hotel, which I’d gonna be in Koreatown.

May 5th, we’re meeting up with some friends and going to the BTS concert in Pasadena. Which is going to be blast.

But we’re staying until May 9th. So the plan is to hit up all the places we can while there.

It’ll be fun!

Jimin skipped to his room, sliding to a halt in front of his door with the words ‘Dancer in the Making’. Jimin smiles at the sign he had since he was at the ripe age of six. Even though that sign was so childish and cute, what he was about to do was completely the opposite of the vibe of his room.

“What are you doing to me, Jimin?”
